room_title: Escape room "Crime Scene" by Master Escape Room in Miami
room_address: 1700 North Dixie Hwy, Boca Raton, FL 33432
room_description: Your special investigations unit was assigned to the Gambini case: a Friday night poker game gone wrong. The cheat was shot and the rest of the players went into hiding. Your task is to search the scene for evidence and find out the identity of the killer.
